  "description": "<p>不管销量如何，三星对Android相机充满了热情。与其他厂商的冷淡相比，国内手机厂商OPPO已经做好进入这个领域的准备了。今天国外媒体曝光了一张OPPO内部的幻灯片，<strong>其内容显示，他们要做一款相机，同时消息还称，该机运行Android系统，支持遥控快门、远程控制功能，并采用了“猫头鹰”图像处理器，主要是提升其在暗光或光线不足下的拍摄能力。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e2edaaa/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243487.htm&amp;t=OPPO%E8%A6%81%E5%81%9AAndroid%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E7%9B%B8%E6%9C%BA%E4%BA%86\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243487.htm&amp;t=OPPO%E8%A6%81%E5%81%9AAndroid%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E7%9B%B8%E6%9C%BA%E4%BA%86\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243487.htm&amp;t=OPPO%E8%A6%81%E5%81%9AAndroid%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E7%9B%B8%E6%9C%BA%E4%BA%86\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243487.htm&amp;t=OPPO%E8%A6%81%E5%81%9AAndroid%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E7%9B%B8%E6%9C%BA%E4%BA%86\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243487.htm&amp;t=OPPO%E8%A6%81%E5%81%9AAndroid%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E7%9B%B8%E6%9C%BA%E4%BA%86\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/email.png\" /></a></td><td valign=\"middle\"></td></tr></table></div><br /><br /><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/165665833629/u/0/f/624776/c/34306/s